cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CV

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning, specifically with topic inference and document classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves deep neural networks, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with information retrieval, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper's use of neural networks for document classification could also suggest cs.CV (Computer Vision).
